						               													<description>Golazo is the action packed football(soccer) board game - easy to learn, but with real tactical depth.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Golazo provides the perfect balance of luck and skill. Win the dice roll and move your counters tactically around the pitch; will you dribble past the defenders, put it out wide for a cross, or find the killer pass that your opponent didn't spot?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Golazo is easy to access: the rules can be picked up in a few minutes and players are always involved.  Gameplay is fast paced, capturing the excitement of a real football match. End-to-end action keeps you on the edge of your seat throughout the whole game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players roll dice against each other and take control of the board to use their moves. Game changing action cards are picked when a 6 is rolled and time is moved on.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
